Set plums inside batter, cut-side up, and sprinkle evenly with cinnamon sugar.
Bake in preheated oven on the lowest rack until a skewer comes out clean, 40 to 50 minutes. Serve warm or cool to room temperature.', '5.0', 'https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/283464/easy-plum-cake/', '/Desserts/Cakes/', 'Total Fat 13g 17%, Saturated Fat 8g 39%, Cholesterol 77mg 26%, Sodium 100mg 4%, Total Carbohydrate 45g 16%, Dietary Fiber 2g 6%, Total Sugars 29g, Protein 4g, Vitamin C 9mg 47%, Calcium 52mg 4%, Iron 1mg 7%, Potassium 193mg 4%', 'Prep Time: 15 mins, Cook Time: 45 mins, Total Time: 1 hrs, Servings: 8, Yield: 1 cake', 'https://www.allrecipes.com/thmb/yRD5Y6Tn9njKyUq5VO441nauIFQ=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/9060371-965f63dfadaf43f5ac8ad3fb0d3ed03e.jpg');
